  "title": "More Piglins with Fresh Animations",
  "description": "Adds new Piglin Variants, now with Fresh Animations.",
  "body": "# More Piglins x [Fresh Animations](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/fresh-animations)\n\n![Banner](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/52af395516c070d200e18eecf95e9917c2b06272.png)\n\n#\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\nThis resource pack adds 6 new variants for both Piglins and Piglin Brutes, and 13 variants for Zombified Piglins!\n\nRequires OptiFine **or** [Entity Model Features](https://modrinth.com/mod/entity-model-features) & [Entity Texture Features](https://modrinth.com/mod/entitytexturefeatures) for Fabric!\n\n<a href=\"https://optifine.net/downloads\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/37507eabcc196eb31e27f1b6349967eceb7008ce_0.webp\" alt=\"OptiFine\" width=\"60\"></a>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d58ec5d489a1814c05e1961ec2a6c5ff122c7910_0.webp\" alt=\"Or\" width=\"50\">\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entity-model-features\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/4I1XuqiY/6e5bbd0d06b1741bfdab6c0cfab6de8fdaf0064c_96.webp\" alt=\"EMF\" width=\"60\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entitytexturefeatures\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/BVzZfTc1/af683d206d50b05258d865b0d6e4aa2f2cee12f2_96.webp\" alt=\"ETF\" width=\"60\"></a>\n\n\n\n\nNew piglins for a new experience!!! Now with Fresh Animation\n\nCheck my profile for more contents ;)",
